*Vode* se u jesen u ribolov. (They go fishing in the autumn.)

Koliko *voda* je potrebno na ovom polju? (How much water is needed in this field?)

Moj otac često *vodi* kućne ljubimce. (My father often walks the pets.)

*Vodu* treba često menjati. (The water must be changed often.)

Dečaci su se igrali u *vodi*. (The boys were playing in the water.)